OLLAMA
1. Dowload Ollama from ollama.com
2. Activate plane mode in Ollama if you are using sensitive info
3. Open a terminal and write ollama pull XXXX
3.1. XXXX is whichever model and version you want to use from ollama.com/library
3.2. Strong recommendation: run "ollama list" and store the ID of the model you downloaded
4. Install ollama library for Python using "pip install ollama"
5. Try running "1_basic.py" and "2_images.py"

OPENAI
0. Get an OpenAI API key via https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
1. Install Python package openai
1.2. Install PIL with pip install pillow
2. Run "5_openai.py"